<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 15:15:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>莫斯科遭受乌克兰猛烈空袭的非凡镜头</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰对莫斯科的大规模打击引发大规模爆炸和火灾，可能预示着远程空战进入了新阶段。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack"&gt;莫斯科遭受乌克兰猛烈空袭的非凡镜头&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 21:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack</guid></item><item><title>HH-60W 直升机变成 VIP 运输机，国会质疑空军的战斗救援准备情况</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports</link><description>&lt;p&gt;显然，HH-60W 机队并不适合太平洋地区，但人们对专用战斗救援能力的担忧与日俱增。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports"&gt;国会质疑 HH-60W 直升机变成 VIP 运输机后空军的战斗救援准备情况&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 20:11:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports</guid></item><item><title>不，一架 VC-25A 空军一号喷气式飞机尚未退役</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet</link><description>&lt;p&gt;前卡塔尔 VC-25B“桥”飞机即将投入使用，但与报道相反，较旧的 VC-25A 将继续飞行。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet"&gt;“不，一架 VC-25A 空军一号喷气机尚未退役”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 18:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet</guid></item><item><title>海军最终寻求处置世界上第一艘核动力巡洋舰长滩号</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser</link><description>&lt;p&gt;拆解一艘核动力战舰比传统动力战舰的成本和时间都要高得多。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser"&gt;海军最终寻求处置世界上第一艘核动力巡洋舰长滩号&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:39:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser</guid></item><item><title>MQ-9 获得机载预警雷达意义重大</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;搭载雷达吊舱的 MQ-9 提供了一种经济且高度灵活的持久机载预警解决方案，现在比以往任何时候都更需要这种解决方案。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal"&gt;MQ-9 获得机载预警雷达是一件大事，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼向乌克兰提供更多爱国者拦截机的能力受到国会质疑（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/pentagons-ability-to-supply-ukraine-with-more-patriot-interceptors-questioned-by-congress</link><description>&lt;p&gt;参议院采取这一行动之际，人们对美国如何为自己和盟友提供足够的爱国者拦截弹深感担忧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/pentagons-ability-to-supply-ukraine-with-more-patriot-interceptors-questioned-by-congress"&gt;国会质疑五角大楼向乌克兰提供更多爱国者拦截机的能力（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 22:59:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/pentagons-ability-to-supply-ukraine-with-more-patriot-interceptors-questioned-by-congress</guid></item><item><title>美国空军订购通用原子公司的 FQ-42 和 Anduril 的 FQ-44 投入生产</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-orders-both-general-atomics-fq-42-and-andurils-fq-44-into-production</link><description>&lt;p&gt;购买两种协同作战飞机设计而不是只选择一种，对于这个仍然是高风险的项目来说有许多巨大的优势。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-orders-both-general-atomics-fq-42-and-andurils-fq-44-into-production"&gt;美国空军订购通用原子公司的 FQ-42 和安杜里尔的 FQ-44 投入生产的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 22:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-orders-both-general-atomics-fq-42-and-andurils-fq-44-into-production</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰将帮助满足欧洲的远程打击导弹需求</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-inks-deal-to-help-fulfill-europes-long-range-strike-missile-needs</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着欧洲寻求更快、更独立的美国远程武器替代品，MBDA 和代傲正在寻求与乌克兰合作。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-inks-deal-to-help-fulfill-europes-long-range-strike-missile-needs"&gt;乌克兰帮助满足欧洲远程打击导弹需求的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 17:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-inks-deal-to-help-fulfill-europes-long-range-strike-missile-needs</guid></item><item><title>参议员希望获得美国空军削减 E-11 BACN 战斗通信机计划的答案</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/senators-want-answers-on-usaf-plans-to-cut-e-11-bacn-combat-communications-jets</link><description>&lt;p&gt;E-11 机队仍然提供高需求的通信和数据融合功能，但美国空军希望将这些功能推向太空。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/senators-want-answers-on-usaf-plans-to-cut-e-11-bacn-combat-communications-jets"&gt;参议员希望获得有关美国空军削减 E-11 BACN 战斗通信机计划的答案，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 16:55:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/senators-want-answers-on-usaf-plans-to-cut-e-11-bacn-combat-communications-jets</guid></item><item><title>据称白宫 UFC 战斗的阴谋使无人机威胁成为人们关注的焦点</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/alleged-plot-on-white-house-ufc-fight-puts-drone-threat-in-the-spotlight</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被捕者是否能够成功实施如此复杂的攻击尚不得而知，但这种威胁是非常真实的，而且还在不断增长。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/alleged-plot-on-white-house-ufc-fight-puts-drone-threat-in-the-spotlight"&gt;据称白宫 UFC 战斗的阴谋使无人机威胁成为人们关注的焦点的帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 22:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/alleged-plot-on-white-house-ufc-fight-puts-drone-threat-in-the-spotlight</guid></item></channel></rss>